Class IDDTruePrivilege

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.informatica.mdm.bpm.idd.IDDTruePrivilege
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPrivilege

    public class IDDTruePrivilege
extends Object
implements IPrivilege
    This implementation of the IPrivilege interface is used to signify that all privileges should be granted. See the IPrivilege interface and the IDDPrivilege class for full details of privileges.
